                                        <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>Download</span>
                                </a>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-body">
            <div class="container has-text-centered">
                <p class="title">
                    Passkey Auth for .NET using Stellar 
                </p>
                <p class="subtitle">
                    Smooth sign in using Passkeys, with integrated robust, secure, and fast account handling using Stellar.
